           String sql = "SELECT * FROM A08_IntegrityFailure";  // Prepare the SQL Query here. Replace with your query or any valid one e,g.: SELECT id,name...from tableName WHERE condition..;    It should be camel case too since it executes queries part of class name convention f and uses methods from JDBC API (Java Database Connectivity)
